n":31761,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ease: The Prophet rebukes Mu\u2019adh for long prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal used to pray with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. Then, he returned to his people and led them in prayer. Mu'adh prayed the evening prayer and recited Surat al-Baqarah, until a man left the prayer, and Mu\u2019adh was critical of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40718,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/07\/07\/exaggerated-recitation\/","url_meta":{"origin":31761,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Recitation: Warning not to exaggerate with the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Mihjan ibn al-Adra\u2019 reported: I was eager to meet the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, one night, and he came out to fulfill one of his needs. The Prophet saw me, took my hand, and we set out. We passed by a man who was praying loudly with\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17436,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/01\/prophet-recite-quran-nawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":31761,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: The Prophet recites Quran before sleep","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 1, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessin